@startuml
autonumber
title "System Sequence Diagram - US01 : Create a Map (with Login)"
actor "Editor" as Editor
participant ":System" as System

activate Editor

Editor -> System: requests to access system
activate System
System --> Editor: displays login screen
deactivate System

Editor -> System: provides username and password
activate System
System --> Editor: grants access to editor interface
deactivate System

Editor -> System: asks to create a new map
activate System
System --> Editor: requests map data (name, width, height)
deactivate System

Editor -> System: inputs requested data
activate System
System --> Editor: shows map data and requests confirmation
deactivate System

Editor -> System: confirms data
activate System
System --> Editor: displays operation success
System --> Editor: displays map details
deactivate System

@enduml